name: 'Power Team, GO!' - a multi-platform game of super heroics!
blurb: Power Team, GO! is a tribute to both classic scrolling arcade games and superhero comics. Gather your team and stop the Forces of Evil!

rewards.reward: 'Thank You' email and listing in the credits as a "Fanboy/Fangirl" in the credits!
Get yourself a copy of the mobile game when it is released on your choice of platform PLUS we'll add you as a "Pal" in the credits!

Wow! Not only do you get the mobile "Power Team, GO!" when it is released, you get our other great game "iSiege:Nuclear Option" as our gift to you to keep you busy in the mean time! PLUS we'll list you as a "Pal" in the credits!
Get a limited edition 12"x18" poster on paper crafted from stardust, wishes and some kind of cotton blend, suitable for framing. PLUS you get all the cool stuff we already mentioned!
Neat-o! A "Power Team, GO!" 4GB USB drive just for you, loaded with free wallpapers for your computer or mobile device. PLUS everything else in the lower tiers!
Show your Hero love with a spiffy t-shirt! PLUS you get all the other stuff at the lower tiers too!

Do you really want to help? Become a beta tester and help us dial in the awesomeness. Sorry- we can ONLY do this for folks with iPHONES and iPADS only due to Android's limited security. We'll even give you everything previously listed PLUS upgrade your status to "Sidekick/Hero Support" in the credits!

Wow, you must love swag, because this tier gives you a "Power Team, GO!" iPhone, iPad, or Android skin PLUS everything else at the lower tiers! Where will you keep it all?! On top of that, we'll upgrade your status in the credits to "Vigilante!"

Nothing like some free publicity! We'll put a cartoon likeness of you in the game on a billboard selling Badger-B-Gon - 'The Badger Eliminator' or a statue in the park! You choose, big spender. PLUS you get everything from the previous tiers.
Build your collection of fine art with a signed original piece of concept or game art! PLUS you get everything previously listed from tier 8 down!

A statue isn't enough? Want to be a part of organized crime? We've got the deal for you! Have your cartoon likeness appear as one of the Rocket Gang characters! PLUS you get everything previously listed from tier 8 down! We'll also upgrade your status in the credits to "Power Team B Squad."

Want to play God but don't have the patience or brainpower to become a Geneticist? Help us design a game play element like a power up, Easter egg or achievement. PLUS get everything from tier 8 down!  We'll also upgrade your status in the credits to "Power Team B Squad."

You ego maniac! That still isn't enough? Alright, we'll design a character and special ability based on your feedback- assuming you keep it sort of clean for the kiddies.  PLUS get everything from tier 8 down! We'll also upgrade your status in the credits to "Power Team A Squad" and send you a unique t-shirt with your character on it!

Heroes are cool and all, but let's face it- villains is where its at!  Assuming we can agree to keep it family-friendly-ish, we'll work with you to design an enemy boss, including his special attacks and abilities!  We'll also upgrade your status in the credits to "Arch Nemesis with Benefits" and send you a unique t-shirt with your character on it!

Holy Cow! You really want this to happen! Choose one item from tiers 9-14 that you'd like to have some creative input on and as our way of saying thanks, we'll send you an iPad2 (or comparable supported Android device) with the game installed with everything unlocked PLUS everything from tier 8 down and we'll add "The Man" or "The Lady" between your first and last names in the credits (your preference-there's no judgement here in Electra City).
